<h1 align="center">Welcome to the Simple IDV</h1>

This version of the IDV has a simpler interface than the
reference application.  It is designed to get you started with
the IDV without exposing the myriad features available in
the entire framework.

Here are some quick links to get your started:<p>

<ul>
<li>Helpful tips on using the IDV are available through the
<a href="jython:idv.getIdvUIManager().showHelpTips ()">Help Tips</a>
<li>Load some sample displays from the 
<a href="jython:idv.getIdvUIManager().showQuicklinksTab('Favorite Bundle');">Favorite Bundles</a> tab in the 
Quick Links.
<li>Choose from a variety of data sources using the
<a href="jython:idv.showChooser()">Data Source Chooser</a>.
</ul>

When you feel comfortable with this simpler IDV, you can 
move up to using the reference application to unleash the
power of the IDV.
</body>

